<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.7">
<l>tattukkoṇ ṭāḷkolō tāṉēpeṟ ṟāḷkolō</l>
<l>citta maṉaiyā ḷacōtai yiḷañciṅkaṅ</l>
<l>kottār karuṅkuḻaṟ kōpāla kōḷari</l>
<l>yattaṉvan tappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉammaṉē yappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did she take [him] in adoption? Or did she herself beget [him]?</l>
<l>The Lord—the young lion of Yaśodā, that woman of intellect,</l>
<l>the murderous lion of the cowherds with black curls full of [flower] clusters—</l>
<l>came and is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
<l>O Mother! He is making [the face of] a hobgoblin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
